{"article_id":"xvfKGbyRBWRTKRXf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"No vice presidential debate has ever swung a presidential race .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"And in 2016 , with two larger-than-life characters at the top of the Republican and Democratic tickets , that truism will surely hold .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"But on the biggest night of their political lives , Gov . Mike Pence","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"( R )","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"of Indiana and Sen. Tim Kaine","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"( D )","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"of Virginia still performed a valuable service for Republican Donald Trump and his Democratic rival , Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"They advanced the story ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"lobbing fresh attacks on each other ' s bosses","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and delving into policy differences .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"For Governor Pence , the debate was a welcome opportunity","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"to move beyond the worst week of the Trump campaign .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Mr. Trump was widely seen as having lost to Mrs. Clinton last week in their first debate ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"and made matters worse","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"by continuing for days to go after a former Miss Universe","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"whom he had once mocked .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Then The New York Times got hold of bits of an old Trump tax return .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Pence faced a barrage of incoming from Senator Kaine ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"and in many cases , declined to defend Trump .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"That , in fact , may have been the smart strategy .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Otherwise , Pence might have spent the entire debate","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"playing defense ,","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"responding to accusations about Trump ' s taxes , admiration for Russian President Vladimir Putin , demeaning comments about women , and birtherism .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"Instead , Pence deflected","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and ignored much of Kaine ' s assault .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"When Kaine asked Pence","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"why he wasn ' t defending Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"Pence replied ,","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"\" I ' m happy to defend him \"","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"- and then continued to not defend him on many of the points .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"When Kaine accused Trump of running an \" insult-driven \" campaign ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"Pence ignored the vast catalog of evidence","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"and turned the slam back on his opponent .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"\" Ours is an insult-driven campaign ? \"","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"Pence interjected , with mock incredulity .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"Then he ran for daylight :","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"What about Clinton","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"calling half of Trump supporters a \" basket of deplorables \" ?","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"Pence countered .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"It was a comeback","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that Trump had failed to make in his debate against Clinton","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"- one of many missed opportunities that night .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"But one by one , Pence checked off those boxes ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"also raising the controversies around Clinton ' s private email server and the family ' s charitable foundation .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"In a way , for Pence , it was a do-over debate","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"- a way","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"to score some points against Clinton","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"that Trump failed to do last week ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and show him how to keep his cool during a debate .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( Clinton and Trump face off again on Oct . 9 . )","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"if Pence has his eye on 2020 ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"as many observers suspect ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"he may well have helped himself .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"At the very least , Pence is now positioned to play a major role","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"in helping the Republican Party pick up the pieces","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"if Trump loses .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"For Kaine , the debate was a chance","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"to unload a torrent of sound bites against a Trump candidacy","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"loaded with vulnerabilities .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"But he came in so aggressive ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and interrupted so much , especially at first ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"that Pence was widely seen as winning on temperament","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"- an important measure","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"of whether a candidate is \" presidential . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" Kaine wins on substance ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"loses on style , \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"wrote independent pollster John Zogby .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Kaine got off some obviously rehearsed one-liners","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"that may turn up in future Clinton campaign ads .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"More than once , he referred to Trump as the \" you ' re fired \" candidate","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"and Clinton , the \" you ' re hired \" candidate .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"And he accused Trump of having a \" personal Mount Rushmore \"","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"President Putin , Kim Jong-un , Muammar Qaddafi , Saddam Hussein .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"The tenor of the debate shifted markedly","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"when the subject of faith came up .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Both men are deeply religious","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"- Kaine is Roman Catholic ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Pence is a born-again Evangelical -","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and they spoke from the heart .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Moderator Elaine Quijano of CBS News asked each to discuss a time","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"when faith conflicted with governing .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Kaine spoke of his struggle , as governor of Virginia , with the death penalty ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"which he opposes .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"\" It was very , very difficult to allow executions to go forward ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"but in circumstances","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"where I did n't feel","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"like there was a case for clemency ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"I told Virginia voters","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"I would uphold the law ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and I did , \"","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Kaine said .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Pence didn ' t offer a similar example ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"and instead used the opportunity","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"to speak on \" the sanctity of life. \"","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"He also offered warm words for Kaine .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"\" I have a great deal of respect for Senator Kaine 's sincere faith .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"I truly do , \"","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"Pence then turned to the Clinton-Kaine ticket ' s support for abortion rights ,","depth":4},{"id":106,"text":"including so-called \" partial-birth abortion \"","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"( which Kaine had , in fact , once opposed ) .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"But it was a respectful critique .","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"And in a campaign","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"nearly devoid of discussion on issues","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"that matter to religious conservatives , a crucial element of the Republican base ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Pence surely in that moment did his ticket some good .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":212,"right":224,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":169,"right":211,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":169,"left":122,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":114,"right":121,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":118,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":115,"right":117,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":7,"right":119,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":123,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":127,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":12,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":13,"right":124,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":153,"right":165,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":148,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":129,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":128,"right":19,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":1